data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful house in River Plantation subdivision. Completely remodeled/renovated home with 2018/2019 appliances. This four bedroom home has the primary bedroom downstairs with en-suite primary bath with lovely remodeled tile shower. Three bedrooms upstairs - great for a family. There is an extra room that could be a formal living area or utilized as an extra space for entertaining. The yard has beautiful landscaping and a sprinkler system.  This neighborhood boasts the amazing River Plantation Golf Course. Come see this amazing home today!
